The right to bare arm!

install:

sudo apt-get install gcc-arm-linux-gnueabi

(assumes that qemu-system-arm is in the path. compile or apt-get...)

see 	http://balau82.wordpress.com/2010/02/28/hello-world-for-bare-metal-arm-using-qemu/
	http://balau82.wordpress.com/2010/12/05/using-ubuntu-arm-cross-compiler-for-bare-metal-programming/
	http://winfred-lu.blogspot.com/2011/12/arm-u-boot-on-qemu.html
